RS ON! KOTOS ONLY!!!<BR />I was thinking I would switch to Jonna's view, riding across the lost plains, going on and on about how her father was going to listen to her after this and let her learn how to use a sword.<img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" /> And chatting away with Squeaky.<img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" /> So, if everyone else is okey-dokey with it, could I take this chapter? At least, I'll try it, but I'm pretty sure I'll be able to get past the limit.<BR />JAMMERS OFF!!!<BR />___<BR />_/  0 /\/ /\/ /-\
                
            
			
