and then if went ahead and went with what you're saying I'd become a mean hypocritical Thomas Jefferson.  (Note: I actually really like Thomas Jefferson, and I don't mean to use him in a bad way, IMO he's a really awesome person.)<BR /><BR />What do you think fellow knights/authors? <BR /><BR />JAMMERS OFF!<BR /> </DIV></BLOCKQUOTE><BR />JAMMERS ON! SAME!!<BR /><BR />Ah, I see. No worries then, just tell me when I'm writing and what view to stick with, and I'll get a chapter up! Of course, if someone else is already writing, then I'll wait. But everyone seems so confused with who's writing when, I think we should just take role call of who's writing, and draw names out of a hat to get the official order. I know I kinda messed it up in the first place, so I'm sorry.<IMG src="/html/images/emoticons/emotion-10.gif" alt="Embarrassed" /><BR /><BR />JAMMERS OFF!!!<BR /><BR />___<BR /><BR />_/&nbsp; 0 /\/ /\/ /-\<BR /><BR /> </DIV></BLOCKQUOTE><BR />JAMMERS ON! SAME!<BR /><BR />Am I still writing? I won't start the chapter until I know for sure. <IMG src="/html/images/emoticons/emotion-4.gif" alt="Stick out tongue" /><BR /><BR />By the way, congrats on Craftsman Jonna! <IMG src="/html/images/emoticons/emotion-2.gif" alt="Big Smile" /><BR /><BR />JAMMERS OOF (<IMG src="/html/images/emoticons/emotion-4.gif" alt="Stick out tongue" />)<BR /><BR /><BR /><BR />-Sharpie: daredevil of lightning </TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></BLOCKQUOTE><BR />JAMMERS ON!<BR /><BR />I think you're still writing. <img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" /> But here's what I think we should do.&nbsp; We should discuss this at our chat forum, keep this place from getting crowded with quote chains. <img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" /><BR /><BR />JAMMERS OFF!<BR />
                
            
			
